title: "Godzilla x Kong: The New Empire"
rating: 5.5
review {
  direction {
    director {
      name: "Adam Wingard"
    }
    rating: "Pretty Bad"
    comments: "Direction (The direction is only good on a macroscale because the movie is only about building this vast mythical world and the massive fight scenes; the direction on a microscale is pretty formulaic and bland as many of the performances just feel like they fill time; the storytelling is not good as the movie does not create a coherent story, it just feels like they force a bunch of plot points together)"
  }
