    rating: "Bad"
    comments: "Story (The concept is so stupid because it just has dumb plot points, like the first 20 minutes of the movie is about how Kong has a toothache; the plot structure is a complete mess as they focus way too much on Kong that this movie feels like Kong ft Godzilla; the character writing for the humans is very shallow and formulaic, the character writing for Godzilla is very shallow as he's just there, the character writing for Kong and the apes is pretty good as its all about finding a home)"
